#Capstone Project: Full VAPT Cycle

##Tools Used
Tool	          Purpose
Kali Linux :	Used as the authorized penetration testing environment
Metasploit Framework :	Used for controlled exploitation simulation in the lab
OpenVAS	: Used to scan and identify vulnerabilities
Google Docs	 : Used for professional report documentation and sharing

##Commands 
Action	                    Purpose
Network reconnaissance :	Identify target system
Vulnerability scanning	: Detect known vulnerabilities
Exploitation simulation	: Validate discovered weaknesses
Evidence logging	: Record findings and timestamps
Remediation verification :	Confirm fixes through rescanning
Report documentation	: Prepare professional PTES report
